e&nbsp;<strong style=\'box-sizing: inherit; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif; font-weight: 700;\'>S</strong>tyle&nbsp;<strong style=\'box-sizing: inherit; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif; font-weight: 700;\'>S</strong>heet) bir css preprocessor&rsquo;udur. 2006 cı ildən&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.hamptoncatlin.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 1 1\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\"><line x1=\\\"0\\\" y1=\\\"0\\\" x2=\\\"1\\\" y2=\\\"1\\\" stroke=\\\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\\" /></svg>\"); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\' target=\"_blank\">Hampton Catlin</a> tərəfindən kodlanmağa başlanılmışdır. SASS ruby dilinə oxşar bir məntiqdə yaradılıb bu dəqiqə də&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/sass/sass\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 1 1\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\"><line x1=\\\"0\\\" y1=\\\"0\\\" x2=\\\"1\\\" y2=\\\"1\\\" stroke=\\\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\\" /></svg>\"); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\' target=\"_blank\">github</a>da inkişaf elətdirilməyi davam etdirilir.</p><p data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-style: normal; word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\'>SASS CSS yazmağı asanlaşdırdığı kimi bizə CSS yazmaq &uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;n fərqli imkanlar yaradır. Dəyişgən təyin etmək(Variables), i&ccedil; i&ccedil;ə yazılmış elementlərin asan oxunulması(nested rules), mixins, imports, if statement, for loop vs. Əslində SASSa bir n&ouml;v CSS programlaşdırma dilidə demək olar.</p><p data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-style: normal; word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\'>Komputerinizə SASS quraşdırmadan işləmək &uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sassmeister.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 1 1\\\" xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\"><line x1=\\\"0\\\" y1=\\\"0\\\" x2=\\\"1\\\" y2=\\\"1\\\" stroke=\\\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\\" /></svg>\"); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\' target=\"_blank\">https://www.sassmeister.com/</a> saytından istifadə edə bilərsiniz.</p><h1 data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, \"Lucida Grande\", \"Lucida Sans Unicode\", \"Lucida Sans\", Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\'>Variables:</h1><p data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-style: normal; word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\