, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif; font-weight: 700;\'><em style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-style: italic;\">// istifadə edilir.</em></strong></p><h1 data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, \"Lucida Grande\", \"Lucida Sans Unicode\", \"Lucida Sans\", Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\'>Mixins:</h1><p data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-style: normal; word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\'>Mixins saytda istfadə edə biləcəyimiz kod qruplarıdır. SASS faylımızda&nbsp;<strong style=\'box-sizing: inherit; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif; font-weight: 700;\'>mixin&nbsp;</strong>təyin edib istədiyimiz yerdə&nbsp;<strong style=\'box-sizing: inherit; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif; font-weight: 700;\'>include&nbsp;</strong>vasitəsi ilə daxil edilir.</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 56px 0px 0px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 20px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\"><span data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 400; display: block; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-style: normal; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, \"Courier New\", Courier, monospace; margin-top: -0.09em; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap;\'>@mixin banner{<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">   width: 100%;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">   position: relative;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">   .banner-content{<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">      position: absolute;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">      width: 100%;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">      top: 50%;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">   }<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">}</span><span data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 400; display: block; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-style: normal; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, \"Courier New\", Courier, monospace; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 1.91em;\'>.lead-banner{<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">   @include banner;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">   text-align: right;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">}</span><span data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 400; display: block; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-style: normal; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, \"Courier New\", Courier, monospace; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 1.91em;\'>.lessons-banner{<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">   @include banner;<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">}</span></pre><h1 data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, \"Lucida Grande\", \"Lucida Sans Unicode\", \"Lucida Sans\", Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\'>Importing Files:</h1><p data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-style: normal; word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\'>SASS yazarkən ən effektiv &uuml;sul hər bir component &uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;n fər