-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\'>Hər bir programlaşdırma dilində olduğu kimi SCSSda da riyazi əməllər vardır. (+,*,-,/)</p><p data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-style: normal; word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\'>Fərz edək ki əlimizdə 6 ədəd li elementi var onları ekran boyunca eyni &ouml;l&ccedil;&uuml; ilə b&ouml;lmək &uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;n:</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 56px 0px 0px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 20px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\"><span data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 400; display: block; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-style: normal; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; line-height: 1.18; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, \"Courier New\", Courier, monospace; margin-top: -0.09em; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap;\'>li{<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"> width( 100% / 6);<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">}</span></pre><h1 data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, \"Lucida Grande\", \"Lucida Sans Unicode\", \"Lucida Sans\", Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\'>Extend:</h1><p data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\'box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-style: normal; word-break: break-word; line-height: 32px; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif; letter-spacing: -0.003em; font-size: 21px;\'>Fərz edək ki bir elementin propertilərini digər bi